description: Residents and tourists in Santiago, Cuba, try to return to normal life after Hurricane Sandy leaves a trail of destruction on its way north. Sandy’s winds and rains were blamed for 11 deaths in Cuba.
title: Cubans and Tourists Recover From Sandy
